{
  "ok": true,
  "taskCredits": 1,
  "caption": [
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:03.880",
      "end_time": "00:00:04.440",
      "text": "Now this, I love!"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:04.441",
      "end_time": "00:00:05.720",
      "text": "We pretty much never talk about UB"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:05.800",
      "end_time": "00:00:08.000",
      "text": "even though we use it all the time in UX design."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:08.160",
      "end_time": "00:00:10.480",
      "text": "So first, UB means user behavior,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:10.520",
      "end_time": "00:00:12.080",
      "text": "it’s user behavior."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:12.120",
      "end_time": "00:00:14.320",
      "text": "And now you’re going to say, “But what’s the difference with UX?”"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:14.360",
      "end_time": "00:00:16.840",
      "text": "Basically, UX or user experience,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:17.040",
      "end_time": "00:00:18.400",
      "text": "is the journey you create,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:18.640",
      "end_time": "00:00:20.160",
      "text": "so the starting intention. And UB,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:20.280",
      "end_time": "00:00:24.840",
      "text": "which we also often call UBA, for user behavior analytics,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:25.120",
      "end_time": "00:00:27.880",
      "text": "is what users actually do in your product,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:27.960",
      "end_time": "00:00:31.040",
      "text": "the reality. And sometimes it’s not the same story at all. When you look at UB,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:31.200",
      "end_time": "00:00:33.320",
      "text": "you mainly look at 3 things: where they get stuck,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:33.440",
      "end_time": "00:00:35.400",
      "text": "what they ignore, and what they do instead."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:35.440",
      "end_time": "00:00:37.360",
      "text": "Basically, you planned a flow A B"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:37.440",
      "end_time": "00:00:39.600",
      "text": "C, and they just go A C"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:39.720",
      "end_time": "00:00:42.280",
      "text": "then leave. And that’s where UB becomes super powerful."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:42.320",
      "end_time": "00:00:45.120",
      "text": "Because once you see what users really do,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:45.240",
      "end_time": "00:00:46.680",
      "text": "you can iterate intelligently."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:46.720",
      "end_time": "00:00:49.640",
      "text": "and you tweak your UX, not based on what you think,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:49.641",
      "end_time": "00:00:51.280",
      "text": "but based on what’s actually happening."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:51.320",
      "end_time": "00:00:52.640",
      "text": "So to make it really simple,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:52.720",
      "end_time": "00:00:55.640",
      "text": "UB shows you the problem and UX lets you fix it."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:55.680",
      "end_time": "00:00:59.040",
      "text": "And it’s this constant iteration between real behavior and"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:59.360",
      "end_time": "00:01:00.160",
      "text": "design intent"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:01:00.520",
      "end_time": "00:01:02.160",
      "text": "that makes your SaaS evolve in the right direction."
    }
  ]
}